--- !u!114 &1920684547
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1920684545}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 79eff4532754d804382167af4bb5ff08, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  speech:
  - HOLY SHIT
  - Now thats how you do it
  - You probably noticed a lot of stuff happening
  - Depending on the stats of your pieces you gain gold, health, and deal damage
    to your enemy
  - On top of this your enemy has a chance to attack back, so be careful
  - Youre basically ready.
  - Keep casting to slowly defeat your enemy
  - Be careful because if you mess up a spell, your enemy will try to take advantage
  - Ill be in the shop. So I wish you good luck in your adventure
  line: 0
  message: 
  textBox: {fileID: 549035312}
  speed: 0.02
  progressBtn: {fileID: 748599380}
  endBtn: {fileID: 1507795261}
